'''Henryk Mikolaj Gorecki''' ({{IPA-pol|ˈxɛnrɨk mʲiˈkɔwaj ɡuˈrɛtski|lang}}, {{lahiamati||6|12|1933||12|10|2010}}) adolah saurang [[pambuek lagu]] [[Polandia]].<ref name=aust>{{Cite web
 |url= http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/arts/polish-composers-greatest-hits-came-late/story-e6frg8n6-1225953446127
 |title=Henryk Gorecki's greatest hits came late | The Australian
 |work=theaustralian.com.au
 |accessdate=3 December 2010
}}</ref> Salah satu karyanyo nan paliang terkenal adolah ''Symphony No. 3'', ''Symphony of Sorrowful Songs'', ditulih pado 1992.<ref name=aust/> Labiah dari satu juta rakaman alah dijua ateh namonyo, dan barasia naik ka paringkek kaanam di tangga lagu [[Inggirih]].<ref name=aust/>

Pada 2010, Gorecki mandapek [[The Order of the White Eagle]], pangharagoan sipil paliang tinggi Polandia.<ref name=aust/>

